column10:
I'll deliver a proper review as I sink more hours into this one. So far:

1) Great anime-style fighter, focusing on striking and obscuring footsies for the most part;

2) Easy to learn, difficult to master;

3) Lively, awsome community - played a couple of matches as a first-timer and actually had opponents allowing for openings mid-match so I could get a handle on things.

So far, solid recommend!
